trans-unit.source: Provides data for a focus-changed event.
trans-unit.target: Disponibiliza dados para um evento alterado o foco.

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.Windows.Automation.AutomationFocusChangedEventArgs"></xref> class.
trans-unit.target: Inicializa uma nova instância do <xref href="System.Windows.Automation.AutomationFocusChangedEventArgs"> </xref> classe.

trans-unit.source: The `idObject` and `idChild` parameters contain the [!INCLUDE[TLA#tla_aa](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)] object identifiers that UI Automation clients can use to link an <xref:System.Windows.Automation.AutomationElement> to an `IAccessible` object in an older accessible technology application.
trans-unit.target: O `idObject` e `idChild` contenham parâmetros de [!INCLUDE[TLA#tla_aa](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)] objeto identificadores que os clientes de automatização de IU podem utilizar para ligar um <xref:System.Windows.Automation.AutomationElement>para um `IAccessible` objeto numa aplicação tecnologia acessível mais antiga.</xref:System.Windows.Automation.AutomationElement>

trans-unit.source: The [!INCLUDE[TLA#tla_id](~/add/includes/tlasharptla-id-md.md)] of the object that received focus.
trans-unit.target: O [!INCLUDE[TLA#tla_id](~/add/includes/tlasharptla-id-md.md)] do objeto que recebeu o foco.

trans-unit.source: The child [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_id](~/add/includes/tla2sharptla-id-md.md)] of the object that received focus.
trans-unit.target: O subordinado [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_id](~/add/includes/tla2sharptla-id-md.md)] do objeto que recebeu o foco.

trans-unit.source: Gets the child [!INCLUDE[TLA#tla_aa](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)] identifier of the object receiving focus.
trans-unit.target: Obtém o subordinado [!INCLUDE[TLA#tla_aa](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)] identificador do objeto receber o foco.

trans-unit.source: Object [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_id#plural](~/add/includes/tla2sharptla-idsharpplural-md.md)] are 32-bit values that identify categories of accessible objects within an application.
trans-unit.target: Objeto [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_id#plural](~/add/includes/tla2sharptla-idsharpplural-md.md)] são valores de 32 bits que identificam as categorias de objetos acessíveis dentro de uma aplicação.

trans-unit.source: The `idObject` and `idChild` parameters contain the object [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_id#plural](~/add/includes/tla2sharptla-idsharpplural-md.md)] that clients can use to link an <xref:System.Windows.Automation.AutomationElement> to an `IAccessible` object in an older accessible technology application.
trans-unit.target: O `idObject` e `idChild` parâmetros de incluir o objeto [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_id#plural](~/add/includes/tla2sharptla-idsharpplural-md.md)] que os clientes podem utilizar para ligar um <xref:System.Windows.Automation.AutomationElement>para um `IAccessible` objeto numa aplicação tecnologia acessível mais antiga.</xref:System.Windows.Automation.AutomationElement>

trans-unit.source: Gets the [!INCLUDE[TLA#tla_id](~/add/includes/tlasharptla-id-md.md)] of the [!INCLUDE[TLA#tla_aa](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)] object that generated the event.
trans-unit.target: Obtém o [!INCLUDE[TLA#tla_id](~/add/includes/tlasharptla-id-md.md)] do [!INCLUDE[TLA#tla_aa](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)] objeto que gerou o evento.

trans-unit.source: Object [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_id#plural](~/add/includes/tla2sharptla-idsharpplural-md.md)] are 32-bit values that identify categories of accessible objects within an application.
trans-unit.target: Objeto [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_id#plural](~/add/includes/tla2sharptla-idsharpplural-md.md)] são valores de 32 bits que identificam as categorias de objetos acessíveis dentro de uma aplicação.

trans-unit.source: The `idObject` and `idChild` parameters contain the object [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_id#plural](~/add/includes/tla2sharptla-idsharpplural-md.md)] that clients can use to link an <xref:System.Windows.Automation.AutomationElement> to an `IAccessible` object in an older accessible technology application.
trans-unit.target: O `idObject` e `idChild` parâmetros de incluir o objeto [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_id#plural](~/add/includes/tla2sharptla-idsharpplural-md.md)] que os clientes podem utilizar para ligar um <xref:System.Windows.Automation.AutomationElement>para um `IAccessible` objeto numa aplicação tecnologia acessível mais antiga.</xref:System.Windows.Automation.AutomationElement>

trans-unit.source: The [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_id](~/add/includes/tla2sharptla-id-md.md)] of the [!INCLUDE[TLA#tla_ui](~/add/includes/tlasharptla-ui-md.md)] element that is receiving focus.
trans-unit.target: O [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_id](~/add/includes/tla2sharptla-id-md.md)] do [!INCLUDE[TLA#tla_ui](~/add/includes/tlasharptla-ui-md.md)] elemento que está a receber o foco.

trans-unit.source: For possible values, see [Object Identifiers](http://msdn.microsoft.com/library/default.asp?url=/library/msaa/msaaccrf_5q05.asp) in the Microsoft Active Accessibility documentation.
trans-unit.target: Para os valores possíveis, consulte [identificadores de objetos](http://msdn.microsoft.com/library/default.asp?url=/library/msaa/msaaccrf_5q05.asp) na documentação do Active Directory acessibilidade da Microsoft.
